Package org.simulator.examples

Class COBRAsolverExample

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.simulator.examples.COBRAsolverExample

  • public class COBRAsolverExample
extends Object
    A simple test class to demonstrate the capabilities of the FBA implementation in Simulation Core Library. This is based on an installation of CPLEX. In order to run this example, it is necessary to launch the JVM with the argument -Djava.library.path=/path/to/the/binaries/of/CPLEX/. Note that this project does not redistribute CPLEX.
    Version:
    1.5
    Author:
    Andreas Dräger, Shalin Shah
